<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Sign Up</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #8bcc8f;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 130px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .signup-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 80%;
        }

        .book-page {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 45%;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .book-page:before,
        .book-page:after {
            content: "";
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-style: solid;
            position: absolute;
        }

        .book-page:before {
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            border-width: 0 25px 25px 0;
            border-color: transparent #f9f9f9 transparent transparent;
        }

        .book-page:after {
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            border-width: 25px 25px 0 0;
            border-color: transparent #f9f9f9 transparent transparent;
        }

        .book-page p {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .signup-box {
            width: 50%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h4 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
        }

        form {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        form label {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        form input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #8bcc8f;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .para-2 {
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .para-2 a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #8bcc8f;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <h2>Recipe & Nutrition Portal Sign Up</h2>
    </div><br><br><br>
    <div class="signup-container">
        <div class="book-page">
            <p>“The best recipes are those where you can feel the chef’s personality and creativity shining through.”</p>
            <p>“Nutrient-rich food is the key to a healthy and fulfilling life.”</p>
        </div>
        <div class="signup-box">
            <h1>Sign Up</h1>
            <h4>to explore recipes and nutrient values</h4>
            <form action="signupsubmit" method="get">
                <label>First Name</label><br>
                <input type="text" name="first_name" placeholder="Your first name" /><br>
                <label>Last Name</label><br>
                <input type="text" name="last_name" placeholder="Your last name" /><br>
                <label>Email</label><br>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email" /><br>
                <label>Password</label><br>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Your password" /><br>
                <label>Confirm Password</label><br>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Confirm your password" /><br><br>
                <button>Submit</button>
            </form>
            <p>
                By clicking the Sign Up button, you agree to our <a href="#">Terms and Conditions</a> and <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>.
            </p>
            <p class="para-2">
                Already have an account? <a href="login.ejs">Login here</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
